      "title": "Rage",
      "description": "As a bonus action, enter a rage that lasts 1 minute. Advantage on STR checks and saving throws. Resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage. Bonus damage on STR melee attacks. Cannot cast or concentrate on spells while raging."
